{
  "text": "One key finding of this work is that weighting techniques are a crucial factor in the overall performance. In the future, we would like to investigate this point more thoroughly, and analyze the interplay of the dataset, the task, the learning algorithm, and the weighting technique more formally and with more exhaustive experimentation. One way to achieve this is by evaluating the embedding using intrinsic measures such as those suggested in [CITATION_1] . Besides, we would like to further investigate how the literals in the dataset can be incorporated while learning the embedding. Furthermore, as GloVe embeddings are known to work particularly well for finding analogies, we plan to adapt the approach for predicting missing links in RDF data sets.",
